Package: bcsnowstats
Title: BC Snow Statistics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Ashlee",
             family = "Jollymore",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "Ashlee.Jollymore@gov.bc.ca"))
Maintainer: Ashlee Jollymore <Ashlee.Jollymore@gov.bc.ca>
Description: This package calculates statistics for snow sites (both automated and manual stations) in British Columbia, Canada. This includes statistics for the period of record (POR), as well as user-defined normal periods.
